        <font color="#000000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Green Leaf Puerh</font></i></b><font color="#000000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br>
        A rare, unusually large loose leaf green Puerh tea from Yunnan province. 
        After plucking, the giant leaves receive minimal processing - a simple 
        withering and sun-drying. The evocative aroma is mellow and earthy and 
        the flavor is rich, full and delicately smoky. A captivating tea that 
        keeps on giving through countless savory infusions.</font></p>
